##Extra student funding

Student loans have to be paid back - grants, bursaries and allowances do not.

<% if calculator.eligible_for_nhs_bursary == "yes" %>
  You can apply for [NHS funding towards your fees and living costs](/nhs-bursaries).
  If you’re on a 4 year accelerated graduate course, you’ll have to apply for an NHS bursary from your second year.
<% elsif calculator.course_studied == "teacher-training" %>
  You can apply for [funding for teacher training](/teacher-training-funding).
<% elsif calculator.course_studied == "social-work" %>
  You can apply for a [Social Work Bursary](/social-work-bursaries).
<% end %>

<% extra_student_funding = [] %>

<% if calculator.eligible_for_childcare_grant_one_child? %>
  <% extra_student_funding << "up to 85% of your childcare costs (maximum #{format_money(calculator.childcare_grant_one_child)} a week for a single child or #{format_money(calculator.childcare_grant_more_than_one_child)} a week if you have more than one) in Childcare Grant" %>
<% elsif calculator.eligible_for_childcare_grant_more_than_one_child? %>
  <% extra_student_funding << "up to 85% of your childcare costs to a maximum #{format_money(calculator.childcare_grant_more_than_one_child)} a week in Childcare Grant if you have 2 or more children" %>
<% end %>

<% if calculator.eligible_for_parent_learning_allowance? %>
  <% extra_student_funding << "up to #{format_money(calculator.parent_learning_allowance)} per year [Parents’ Learning Allowance](/parents-learning-allowance)" %>
<% end %>

<% if calculator.eligible_for_adult_dependant_allowance? %>
  <% extra_student_funding << "up to #{format_money(calculator.adult_dependant_allowance)} per year [Adult Dependant’s Grant](/adult-dependants-grant)" %>
<% end %>

<% if calculator.uk_ft_circumstances.include?('has-disability') || calculator.uk_all_circumstances.include?('has-disability') %>
  <% extra_student_funding << "[Disabled Students’ Allowance](/disabled-students-allowances-dsas)" %>
<% end %>

<% if calculator.uk_ft_circumstances.include?('low-income') || calculator.uk_all_circumstances.include?('low-income') %>
  <% extra_student_funding << "[University and college hardship funds](/extra-money-pay-university/university-and-college-hardship-funds) (extra help with costs while studying)" %>
<% end %>

<% unless extra_student_funding.empty? %>
  Depending on your income and circumstances, you could get:

  <%  extra_student_funding.each do |funding|  %>
  - <%=  funding  %>
  <%  end  %>
<%  end %>

<% if calculator.uk_ft_circumstances.include?('low-income') || calculator.uk_all_circumstances.include?('low-income') %>
  You could get a [bursary or scholarship](/extra-money-pay-university) from your university or college.
<% else %>
  You could get a [bursary, scholarship or financial hardship funding](/extra-money-pay-university) from your university or college.
<% end %>

You might be able to get [help with the costs of travel for study or work placements](/travel-grants-students-england) as part of your course.

Use the [Turn2us grant search](http://grants-search.turn2us.org.uk/) to check whether you qualify for funding from a charitable trust.
